{"id": 1900, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你看过哪些关于戾气的误解？", "description": "为什么普通的维权和批评就被当成了“戾气”？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 11176, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170911162244O4wdSIZ6XAG1cjpC.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-12T17:00:13Z", "questions": [{"id": 2953, "title": "现如今，你看过哪些关于戾气的误解？", "content": "现如今，你看过哪些关于戾气的误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 234809, "content": "关心公共事务，提了一些自己的看法就被认为是瞎抱怨、负能量", "image": "img/option/option/20170911180259xDyp0UEnkTMmaeAK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234808, "content": "争取工作中的个人福利，被说年轻人挑三拣四怎么都不满意", "image": "img/option/option/20170911175439qZnrDtdJQ4h30Olk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234806, "content": "批评演员演技，被粉丝围攻“你这个喷子、键盘侠你行你上”", "image": "img/option/option/20170911174611wasQMcHf3ViuSxpP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234807, "content": "支持反抄袭的作者维权，被指“揪着一个点不放、抠字眼”", "image": "img/option/option/20170911174915gdSeO6haAQw1F3Mv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234811, "content": "说了两句国产电影不好，被扣上崇洋媚外、打压国产电影的帽子", "image": "img/option/option/20170912135302uMy1J3fotkHbDE0K.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234812, "content": "看到和性别不平等、刻板印象有关的事情就指出来，被认为事儿多、玻璃心", "image": "img/option/option/20170912140051MLvCtfk5G8YBUsgQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234813, "content": "批评公共场合抽烟或者小孩子吵闹被认为不能理解别人，太龟毛", "image": "img/option/option/201709121402358QpHvzKoyluRMOXF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234826, "content": "道歉之后就不能再追究了：我都道歉了你怎么还盯着我？", "image": "img/option/option/20170912140248OS68a1nortdCgcUE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}